Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.62,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:08.86,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for calling you out on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.80,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect Menma's father would get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.58,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why we're going there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:19.43,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,We can corner Menma's mom while her dad is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:22.61,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Her mom will definitely side with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.70,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:28.15,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,She even gave us Menma's diary. I'm sure she'd do anything for Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:30.21,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:33.97,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If she knew I went to her house again without telling her anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:36.53,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'd be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.17,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:15.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Atsumu and Chiriko came too this time. I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.92,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.20,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.86,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:19.86,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.20,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.20,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So is this about the rocket firework?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.40,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when my husband first told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.13,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends all gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.84,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And you come up with fun ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as when you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:45.95,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when we were kids we actually planned to make fireworks with Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really. Meiko was involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:54.86,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If we could launch fireworks, I think that Menm... I mean, Meiko would also be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So we'd like you to ask your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:02.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You all sure do get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.33,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:09.08,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Meiko must be so envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She was left out by her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:20.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You may talk about what Meiko would enjoy, but really you're just having fun yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.92,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're using Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.53,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.56,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:28.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Meiko's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:34.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you all go on the same as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.08,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:43.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you playing with Meiko on that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:44.60,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You read her diary didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Time has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.16,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one who hasn't changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:57.34,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But why have you all grown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:01.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Meiko the only one... Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Only her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.86,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.69,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.20,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.91,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is your hand okay, Tsurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.07,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's mom was super scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:30.87,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Maybe she's resented us all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:38.06,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the first time someone has hated me this strongly since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.66,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,She's a parent after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.26,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.24,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:49.13,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drop this foolishness about Menma's wish already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.43,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second. If we do that we don't know what will happen to Menm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:58.10,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has been playing along with poor pitiful you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.64,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.49,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I took it too far myself, so I can't exactly judge others in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:08.99,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike you, I don't force my own pain onto others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.27,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,My own pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.99,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the right way to put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:17.54,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're obsessed with the past, and even Menma's parents are like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.97,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:24.63,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,He was talking about himself wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.58,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's in pain is Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:35.80,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you Jintan. I believe that Menma's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.18,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.11,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grant it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.73,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.94,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But you said that all of us together have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.82,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.37,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought that everyone had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:48.96,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:54.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But once I spoke to everyone, I was surprised that no one had changed all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.87,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how little we change, we're not all together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.84,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,We never were from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:09.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Because Menma is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.62,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:14.25,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Since all of us together don't exist anymore, it's all the same if I grant the wish on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:21.46,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait Jintan! I'll keep helping like I have been, so we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.39,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.55,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.97,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I was taking my shoes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.70,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I can grant it even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.05,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What? You signed up for even more hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:53.16,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Construction pays well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.04,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I haven't slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.15,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.35,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,All I did with my life until now was sleep and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I've built up a big sleep surplus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.17,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.97,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How can he put so much energy into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.09,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does he care about Menma that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.25,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Wh.. Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.85,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.54,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.66,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,And take this multivitamin too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:30.72,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:36.96,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.44,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.75,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.44,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.99,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You must be in a lot of pain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.95,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.25,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by 'this'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.19,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.87,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I still have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.38,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.25,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.25,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.78,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to go back then either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.17,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:17.72,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you something terrible about myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.80,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:23.97,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was actually relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.32,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you didn't like Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.35,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's horrible of me, but I was actually kind of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.26,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.82,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,When you left like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:49.17,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same as you saying you loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.26,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,That moment has pained me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:58.39,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive myself for being happy then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:02.35,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Or for hurting Menma, and for how it all ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:08.50,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I... I couldn't forgive myself for liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:16.00,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But it turns out that I... I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.05,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.30,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're being strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:38.89,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Say that Menma really is at your house, if you grant her wish, won't she disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:44.30,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fine with her disappearing, even though you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.61,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan you're an...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:01.16,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.51,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.61,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Was she waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.15,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Your nails are pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.84,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean them off with toothpicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.81,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:38.63,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Once I grant her wish, Menma will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:39.25,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:41.93,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, bear it for just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:51.11,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's what Menma wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:56.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the way it is, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.41,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.55,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Did it hurt that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:14.89,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No I... I remembered The Dog of Flanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.66,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:18.45,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about Patrasche.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.45,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Patrasche?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:26.03,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,They were showing a rebroadcast of The Dog of Flanders a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:30.06,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying? This is such a crappy lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.10,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.33,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:37.80,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan!        I'm sure that Patrasche was happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.01,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:45.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nello was really, really nice to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.29,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,They were friends. So it's fine right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.99,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.06,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:26.93,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's mother continues to hate us because she lost Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.41,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru continues blame herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And Yukiatsu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.13,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And probably Tsuruko as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And even Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:41.28,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No one is being saved from their sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:46.16,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I can see Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.70,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only being saved by Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.16,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That's so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.12,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:02.61,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.30,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.94,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.30,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Today is your mother's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.99,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.16,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.73,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the only one who can see Menma,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:33.34,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,then I have a duty to fulfill her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.56,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's rusted over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{women talk in the background here, I can't catch it well enough to bother with a tl}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.02,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.89,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.00,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.30,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:10.91,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't say a thing about me not going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.74,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe he'd gotten fed up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:16.98,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.41,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.09,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:26.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.60,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.60,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it's about your job then don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.41,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.10,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no way, what is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:40.30,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about going to the Honmas? Which one is it? Neither of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.13,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You know about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.35,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:51.50,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I couldn't tell what you were apologizing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.01,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.05,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.37,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Bring that incense over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.40,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:07.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't underestimate a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:13.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Jintan left without even saying good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.02,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That's Poppo's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.17,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:25.61,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how Menma's mom reacted, we can't leave Jintan to do everything on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:30.60,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,And here I'd thought the Super Peace Busters had finally gotten back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.40,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.54,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,So I believe in Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.62,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Jintan is the only one who can see her, and even if no one else believes in her, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.52,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.00,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're getting silent phone calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.23,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:59.15,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yadomi is at work right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.64,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. You don't think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:05.85,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,The caller ID showed Yadomi's home phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.89,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi is making prank calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:13.05,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,There was a kind of scraping, sandy noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:17.85,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,This might sound silly, but what if it wasn't Yadomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:18.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.65,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:30.93,Default,Manage,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Anjou wouldn't take days off without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:31.93,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.13,Default,Manage,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.93,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.86,Default,Manage,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Dang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.94,Default,Manage,0000,0000,0000,,I had plans for muscle party with everyone from the gym today. {I don't know what a muscle party is, but I'm sure people can imagine}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.09,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how I should act towards Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,When I see her next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.35,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.07,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.44,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:01.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one who should be sorry for intruding on your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.90,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.67,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,My mom usually doesn't leave the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.73,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I think she doesn't want to see other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:15.55,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's hard for her because my sister passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.08,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,But it's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:22.53,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Or how could I put it... it's embarrassing to have a mother like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:26.23,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are parents thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.36,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:29.82,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's hardest for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Because parents are, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.99,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you don't have to tell me all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.78,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,They still have another child left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:51.86,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I was still a little kid, so I don't really remember my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:56.17,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a few things I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:58.43,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.88,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.31,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.62,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.60,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.27,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:12.25,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I'm in the Super Peace Busters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:20.57,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect world peace! So you stay here and protect the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.74,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.16,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.59,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to protect the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.30,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,But who'd want something from that stingy dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.54,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.87,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anjou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.56,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jintan showed up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.90,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:03.31,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What? I've been at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:09.25,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been calling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.98,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:14.56,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I got a silent phone call around 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.12,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:20.03,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What about it? Are you going to say it was Menma again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:21.72,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:27.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and I were both out of the house then, so maybe Menma really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:32.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? You keep blabbering "Menma, Menma".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:33.76,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.03,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.82,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:43.76,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show her to me too. Menma is there right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.04,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Show her to me if she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.48,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.89,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.55,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:56.44,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.25,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.36,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not that again....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.60,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.26,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst. You're keeping this act about seeing Menma's ghost even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:16.74,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.49,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.55,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.93,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.44,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Is Menma there Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.56,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You stop it too Poppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.59,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.59,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan, time out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.16,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.90,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you. I'm begging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:46.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:52.23,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The things we did to Menma won't fade for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.03,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Menma apologizing to us is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.99,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Menma could forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.57,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,The diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:08.29,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why? There's no wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.61,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:15.01,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Really, why did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.21,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong Popo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:29.81,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Today I played at the secret fort with everyone who had grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:34.72,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:39.57,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,The Super Peace Busters should always get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.37,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.29,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is Menma's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:48.45,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's Menma's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.03,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.34,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma... Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.75,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:59.56,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.42,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
