Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:32.04,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\3cH8789E8}{\an8}zutto kimi wo sagashiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.17,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\3cH8789E8}{\an8}souyatte ima wa boku no hou e
