Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.62,0:00:47.38,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon pages and pages of entries
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.79,0:00:51.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,We've put down all our emotions
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.09,0:00:54.84,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I've hit a writer's block
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.09,0:00:58.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to finish this page anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.05,0:01:01.97,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting a bookmark in my diary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.64,0:01:07.06,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I go out to ride the bike we found in the dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.23,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to our secret place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.27,0:01:14.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we piled up our bricks of memories
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.36,0:01:19.78,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Run up the hill, where we can see the horizon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.83,0:01:24.37,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we can see the sky so fearfully blue
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.58,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,With cider in my right hand
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.58,0:01:32.04,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,My other hand helps me search for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.17,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to come find me way back when
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.84,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to demand me of so much more
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.84,0:01:46.64,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both still standing right by my side
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.02,0:01:54.44,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet why do I pray to see you both again?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.65,0:02:02.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something off with me
