Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:19.51,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kimi to natsu no owari shourai no yume ookina kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:26.60,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}jyuunen no ato hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
