Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:19.51,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams \Nwe shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:26.60,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we will meet again in another \NAugust, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:33.82,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:36.61,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know it must've been painful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:40.87,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:50.49,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}But those are my best memories.
